   Form for API keys / OAuth credentials used by other modules:
   - Anthropic (marketing newsletter)
   - MailerLite (marketing list)
   - Sender identity (from name/email)
   - Google OAuth (Gmail send-as)

   Values come from core_config_data via the same paths the runtime
